(56, 1, '2014-12-08 17:24:28', '2014-12-08 17:24:28', '<h1>Membership</h1>\r\n<p>The Paget’s Association is the only UK charity dedicated solely to those with Paget’s disease. Our Free Online Membership of the Paget’s Association offers you support in the following ways:</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Access the member only area of our website for articles, newsletters, detailed information about Paget’s disease, investigations and treatment</li>\r\n<li>A quarterly informative member newsletter via email</li>\r\n<li>Paget’s Support Network is available only to members and enables you to contact others who have Paget’s disease</li>\r\n<li>Evidence based written publications</li>\r\n<li>Meetings for members, giving the opportunity to hear presentations from experts in Paget’s disease, raise questions and meet with one another</li>\r\n<li>A dedicated Nurse Helpline managed by our Specialist Paget’s Nurse</li>\r\n<li>An annual members’ day</li>\r\n<li>Access to local contacts and support groups where possible</li>\r\n<li>As a member you are supporting research into the prevention, causes and treatment of the disease</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Membership', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'membership', '', '', '2014-12-10 22:57:17', '2014-12-10 22:57:17', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/?page_id=56', 8, 'page', '', 0),
