(362, 1, '2014-12-10 16:40:41', '2014-12-10 16:40:41', '<p>The Paget’s Association accepts secure direct on-line donations and payments through PayPal, you do not need to have a PayPal account to donate using either a credit or debit card.</p>\r\n<p>If you would like the Paget’s Association to reclaim tax on the donations you make until further notice you need to click on the link ‘ Can we claim Gift Aid on your donation?’ at the end of the Paypal payment process.</p>\r\n<p>Please donate by clicking on the button below</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input name="cmd" type="hidden" value="_s-xclick" /> <input name="hosted_button_id" type="hidden" value="93S5VL4QNL434" /> <input alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online." name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/WEBSCR-640-20110429-1/en_US/GB/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" type="image" /> <img src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/WEBSCR-640-20110429-1/en_GB/i/scr/pixel.gif" alt="Donate" width="1" height="1" border="0" /></form></p>\r\n<p> <a href="http://www.justgiving.com/narpd/donate">Donate via justgiving.com</a></p>', 'Online Payments', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'online-payments', '', '', '2014-12-11 23:43:49', '2014-12-11 23:43:49', '', 45, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/?page_id=362', 1, 'page', '', 0),
