(417, 1, '2014-12-10 22:50:13', '2014-12-10 22:50:13', '<h1>Membership</h1>\n<p>The Paget’s Association is the only UK charity dedicated solely to those with Paget’s disease.\nOur Free Online Membership of the Paget’s Association offers you support in the following ways:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Access the member only area of our website for articles, newsletters, detailed information about Paget’s\ndisease, investigations and treatment</li>\n• A quarterly informative member newsletter via email\n• Paget’s Support Network is available only to members and enables you to contact others who have\nPaget’s disease\n• Evidence based written publications\n• Meetings for members, giving the opportunity to hear presentations from experts in Paget’s disease,\nraise questions and meet with one another\n• A dedicated Nurse Helpline managed by our Specialist Paget’s Nurse\n• An annual members’ day\n• Access to local contacts and support groups where possible\n• As a member you are supporting research into the prevention, causes and treatment of the disease', 'Membership', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '56-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-12-10 22:50:13', '2014-12-10 22:50:13', '', 56, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/uncategorized/56-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(418, 1, '2014-12-10 22:51:05', '2014-12-10 22:51:05', '<h1>Membership</h1>\r\n<p>The Paget’s Association is the only UK charity dedicated solely to those with Paget’s disease. Our Free Online Membership of the Paget’s Association offers you support in the following ways:</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Access the member only area of our website for articles, newsletters, detailed information about Paget’s disease, investigations and treatment</li>\r\n<li>A quarterly informative member newsletter via email</li>\r\n<li>Paget’s Support Network is available only to members and enables you to contact others who have Paget’s disease</li>\r\n<li>Evidence based written publications</li>\r\n<li>Meetings for members, giving the opportunity to hear presentations from experts in Paget’s disease, raise questions and meet with one another</li>\r\n<li>A dedicated Nurse Helpline managed by our Specialist Paget’s Nurse</li>\r\n<li>An annual members’ day</li>\r\n<li>Access to local contacts and support groups where possible</li>\r\n<li>As a member you are supporting research into the prevention, causes and treatment of the disease</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Membership', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-10 22:51:05', '2014-12-10 22:51:05', '', 56, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/uncategorized/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
