(452, 1, '2014-12-11 22:34:37', '2014-12-11 22:34:37', '<p>This is a 56 page, A4 booklet containing 18 articles, written by professionals and experts in Paget’s disease. These articles include information regarding diagnosis, treatment, side-effects, bone deformity, hearing loss, diet, exercise, bone cancer, research and archaeological findings regarding Paget’s disease. This booklet will be particularly interesting to those recently diagnosed. Initially written for members of the Association, the articles have all been previously published in either “Paget’s News”* or on this website. They are now available to everyone in this handy collection.<br /> <small>* The “Paget’s News” is the newsletter published for members of the Paget’s Association</small></p>', 'Paget’s Disease: A selection of 18 articles PDF version', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pagets-disease-selection-18-articles-pdf-version', '', '', '2014-12-11 23:03:18', '2014-12-11 23:03:18', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/?post_type=product&#038;p=452', 0, 'product', '', 0),
