(458, 1, '2014-12-11 23:14:07', '2014-12-11 23:14:07', '<h1>Remember Someone</h1>\r\n<p>Losing someone you love is one of the hardest experiences that most of us will ever go through. People often feel the need to recognise and celebrate the life of that person in a way which is fitting and meaningful and for many years the Paget''s Association has been the recipient of donations given in memory of a loved one.</p>\r\n<p>Up until now all we could do to thank people for thinking about the Association was to include the name of the loved one in the In Memoriam box in the newsletter and send a letter of thanks. Now it will be possible to create your own memoriam to your loved in our new Remembrance Garden on our website.</p>', 'Remember Someone', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-11 23:14:07', '2014-12-11 23:14:07', '', 78, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/uncategorized/78-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
