(482, 1, '2014-12-11 23:44:28', '2014-12-11 23:44:28', '<p>The Paget’s Association has signed up to a free text donation service provided by JustTextGiving which enables you to make small donations up to a maximum of £10 via a simple text from any network.  The Association receives 100% of the donation. </p>\r\n<p>To make a donation using this method please put PPAO22 in the message box, add the amount you wish to donate and text to 70070.  You will then be given the opportunity to Gift Aid your donation thereby increasing its value by 25% at no additional cost to you.  You will receive a text acknowledgement of your donation.</p>\r\n<p>(Add the mobile phone image off the current website please)</p>', 'By Text', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '364-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-11 23:44:28', '2014-12-11 23:44:28', '', 364, 'http://92.60.114.159/~pagetorg/uncategorized/364-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
